A monstrous pact
Firez's army is very strong and attacking his stronghold with only Canian troops is too risky. Tui-Len knows a way to subjugate wild monsters. If you can capture a few strong monsters for help, you can attack the last refuge of the enemy.
#subobj 1
Subdue the cyclops
The participation of a cyclops in battle on the Canian side can decide the outcome of a battle. In order to subjugate a cyclops, you must approach it with the amulet.
#subobj 2
Subjugate your dragon
A dragon can provide invaluable service and tip the balance of victory in Canian's favour. To subdue a dragon, approach it with an amulet.